# Keeps this dir tracked. The 356MB wavlm_large_int8.onnx is gitignored (>100MB,
# GitHub limit). It is the local-first, on-device embedder — download it here as
# wavlm_large_int8.onnx (see README "Running locally"):
#   https://drive.google.com/file/d/1O4uoKIUKnGPzNopkYlcqvO08TeS71-_h/view?usp=sharing
#   gdown 1O4uoKIUKnGPzNopkYlcqvO08TeS71-_h -O wavlm_large_int8.onnx
# If absent, the xgboost service falls back to the Fireworks embedding API
# (set FIREWORKS_API_KEY + FIREWORKS_MODEL).
